comments: Dr. Gillie is a respectful and kind teacher. She is tougher, only because she wants us to try our best. She is a very lenient grader, and is always willing to help.
I LOVED this class. By far my favorite course. Dr. Gillie is the bomb! Great teacher, and super caring about her students learning. Kind of difficult, but worth every second.

I advise no one to take this class. She is like a middle school teacher looking for someone to punish. Also takes music 101 too far for people only trying to take as a pre req. stay away if you can!!!
Dr. Gillie takes the fear out of Ear Training and makes it an enjoyable subject. She is very in-tune (no pun intended) with student life and is very understandable.
Dr. Gillie is fantastic! Great energy and teaches concepts clearly. She makes ear training WAY less scary!
Professor Gillie is just like a student. She\'s young and fun and totally approachable. Ear training can often be scary but she makes it not seem so bad.
